{"word":"ἀνασπαστός","slug":"ἀνασπαστός","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<entryFree id=\"n7497\" key=\"a)naspasto/s\" type=\"main\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"entryFree\"> <orth extent=\"suff\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">ἀνα-σπαστός</orth>, <itype lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"itype\">όν</itype>, <sense id=\"n7497.0\" n=\"A\" level=\"1\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">drawn up,</tr_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0019.tlg004.perseus-grc1:382\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Ar.\">Ar.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ V.\">V.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">382</biblScope> </bibl>: but mostly, <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">dragged up the country,</tr_> of tribes compelled to emigrate into Central Asia, <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ἀνασπαστοὺς ποιῆσαι τοὺς Παίονας ἐς τὴν Ἀσίην</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0016.tlg001.perseus-grc1:5:12\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Hdt.\">Hdt.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">5.12</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">τούτους ἐξ Αἰγύπτου ἀ. ἐποίησαν παρὰ βασιλέα</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0016.tlg001.perseus-grc1:4:204\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Id.\">Id.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">4.204</biblScope></bibl></cit>, cf. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0016.tlg001.perseus-grc1:6:9\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">6.9</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0016.tlg001.perseus-grc1:32\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">32</biblScope> </bibl>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">τοὺς ἀ. κατοικίζειν</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0016.tlg001.perseus-grc1:3:93\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Id.\">Id.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">3.93</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">εὐθὺς ἀ.</foreign> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">removing</tr_> hastily, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0543.tlg001.perseus-grc1:2:53:5\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Plb.\">Plb.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">2.53.5</biblScope></bibl>. </sense> <sense n=\"2\" id=\"n7497.1\" level=\"3\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> of a door or gate, <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">drawn back, opened</tr_> from inside, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0011.tlg002.perseus-grc1:1186\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ S.\">S.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Ant.\">Ant.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1186</biblScope></bibl>. </sense> <sense n=\"II\" id=\"n7497.2\" level=\"2\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> as <pos opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"pos\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Subst.\">Subst.</a></pos>, <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">οἱ ἀ.</foreign> (sc. <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἱμάντες</foreign>) <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">latchets,</tr_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0008.tlg001.perseus-grc1:12\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Ath.\">Ath.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">12</biblScope></bibl>. <pb n=\"121\" TEIform=\"pb\"/> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0008.tlg001.perseus-grc1:543f\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">543f</biblScope></bibl>.</sense> </entryFree>"}]}